## [Latest Version]
### Added
- Added Python to Docker image for serving the web UI.
- Added `run.sh` script to start Ollama service and serve the web UI.
- Included a web interface to list available models and interact with the loaded model.
- Added HTML and JavaScript to provide the functionality of sending chat prompts to the model.
- Defined ingress support to make the add-on available directly from Home Assistant UI.

### Changed
- Modified Dockerfile to include installation of Python.
- Updated `run.sh` to declare and assign configuration values separately to avoid masking return values.